data.description: Welcome to your dream home on beautiful Harbour Island in Tampa, Florida! This stunning 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence comes with a garage which is hard to come by in an urban setting. With a central location this community offers a luxurious and convenient lifestyle in one of the city's most coveted locations. The living area is spacious and ideal for both relaxation and entertaining. The unit comes upgraded with wood floors, stainless steel appliances, and a balcony to enjoy the beautiful Florida weather. The barrel tile roof on the entire community was recently replaced. The master bedroom is generously sized and offers a peaceful retreat from the bustling city. The second bedroom is also spacious and well-appointed, providing comfort and privacy for family members or guests. Living on Harbour Island means you'll have access to a host of amenities Water Street, Amalie Arena, Sparkman Wharf, and Downtown Tampa. Take advantage of the community's swimming pool, fitness center, and beautifully landscaped common areas. Additionally, this location offers easy access to downtown Tampa, where you can explore an array of shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom townhome with a garage on Harbour Island in Tampa, Florida. Experience the ultimate in luxury, comfort, and convenience while having the space that most do not have.
